Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Fullmetal Alchemist,0000,0000,0000,,Brotherhood
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Fullmetal Alchemist,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 9
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Fullmetal Alchemist,0000,0000,0000,,===============================================================

Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:40.25,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Ed and Al infiltrated the former Research Laboratory 5,\Nseeking the secret of the philosopher's stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.25,0:01:44.87,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,There, they encountered people who had their souls affixed to suits of armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:58.86,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Due to what Number 66 said during their battle, Al started to question whether he was a faux soul, created by Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.40,0:02:06.56,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're able to get up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:10.24,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Research Laboratory 5?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:11.65,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:14.82,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,It was blown up by someone and has been completely destroyed...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:17.65,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!!! It's all gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:21.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.03,0:02:23.66,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:27.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I was so close to the "truth", too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.36,0:02:30.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be sitting in a hospital like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.61,0:02:34.28,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Fullmetal Alchemist!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:37.05,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We apologize for the rudeness in advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:38.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.16,0:02:47.87,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,Doing whatever you wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:50.35,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,If things had gone badly, you would have died!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:56.57,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of trying to do everything by yourselves, rely on the people around you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.76,0:03:03.78,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't hurt to trust your elders, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:09.21,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,That is all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:13.83,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive our rude language and violence toward a higher-ranking officer, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:17.76,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:19.84,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,My fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:23.87,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,Punishment... for the slap, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.56,0:03:26.02,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No, I wouldn't dream of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:29.43,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you guys try to be so considerate around me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:33.50,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,Because being a State Alchemist is equivalent to being a Major in the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:38.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get my state qualification for something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.02,0:03:41.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You guys don't need to be so polite to me, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:42.69,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:45.07,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, all those times have been a waste, haven't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:46.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What a quick change!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:50.10,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... now that I think about it, where's Al?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:54.64,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,I scolded him with a fist earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:56.75,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:04:01.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot about the other person who's going give me a scolding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:10.97,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? You've reached the Rockbells,\Nspecializing in prosthetics and orthotics.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.34,0:04:13.10,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Ed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:16.10,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,It's rare for you to call.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.10,0:04:18.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:20.56,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This is extremely difficult for me to say, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:23.59,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind taking a trip to Central for a little maintenance?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:24.73,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:25.43,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:27.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's my right arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:31.33,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,My fingers move, but I can't lift my arm at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:38.56,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,So it was no good, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:39.10,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:40.83,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:44.13,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do something before your arm stopped moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:48.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was in an all-out brawl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.91,0:04:53.60,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,AGAIN?! Quit using my automail for things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:05:00.17,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,H... Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.64,0:05:02.62,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Winry?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:04.17,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:05.61,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Where in Central?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:09.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're kind of nice tod-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:12.65,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.65,0:05:14.21,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:16.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:17.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:18.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:21.79,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,A love call to your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.79,0:05:24.05,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who's my girlfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:27.62,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,How boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:29.41,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,When I was your age, I had...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:30.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:33.19,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:35.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:37.37,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:39.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Want to head to our room?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:44.74,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:47.90,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:48.99,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I'll meet you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:50.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:12.22,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:21.52,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,...maybe you're an armor doll that your "brother" created?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:33.13,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Oww, my rear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.13,0:06:35.79,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see how Ed and Al can ride these things all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.97,0:06:43.42,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,He said there'd be someone waiting for me at the\Nwest gate, and I'd be able to spot him right away, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:45.42,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:47.63,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Major Armstrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.79,0:06:52.36,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Miss Winry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.17,0:06:56.10,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Where are those stupid Elric brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.97,0:06:59.64,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:07.69,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Ed's in the hospital?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:12.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:16.02,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're planning on charging me a rush fee, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:22.94,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,But... you were injured this badly when your automail broke, because I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:25.63,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,...I didn't equip it properly, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:32.13,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not your fault or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:38.15,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who used it recklessly,\Nand the maintenance was perfect, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:42.98,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't notice the missing screw?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:47.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,And there's also the fact I didn't have to get hurt more because my arm broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:50.61,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry about it! Yeah? Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:52.99,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,So it all works out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:57.53,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, so about this maintenance trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:07:59.93,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,On second thought, I'll be charging a rush fee!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:00.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:05.54,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't drink your milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:09.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I... don't like milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:13.51,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why you're so short!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:14.58,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:16.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help that I don't like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:20.56,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,You're being picky, Edward Elric!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:23.08,Default,Ross,0000,0000,0000,,All the kids drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:24.77,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get any girls if you can't drink milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:27.87,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:38.70,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al's been acting strange lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:42.20,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:46.20,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Seems to me something's on his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:04.47,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,...maybe you're an armor doll that your "brother" created?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:07.23,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Just accept it. It'll make you feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:17.36,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,There! Maintenance complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:19.53,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:21.94,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:23.63,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.63,0:09:25.05,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:28.38,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:31.09,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,So I heard you're kind of occupied after bringing a woman into your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:35.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,She's just my automail mechanic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:38.59,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... so you sweet-talked your mechanic, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:42.43,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,When I say one thing, you come up with another!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.75,0:09:44.98,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Maes Hughes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:45.89,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:48.11,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Winry Rockbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.11,0:09:50.63,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you get in trouble for ditching work?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:52.65,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:54.99,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,I left Sheska with overtime work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:57.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, a demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:10:01.85,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, you guys are almost free from your escorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:03.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:04.62,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Escorts?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:06.52,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:09.00,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Just what kind of dangerous situations are you getting yourself into?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:12.92,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Well, look. How should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:17.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:26.29,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:29.44,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,You two never tell me anything, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:33.27,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:37.10,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go look for a place to stay for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:38.03,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:40.32,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Then stay at my place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:41.55,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:43.08,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:44.88,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,My wife and daughter will be delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.88,0:10:45.43,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:46.85,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,All right, it's settled!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.85,0:10:48.13,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:49.60,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:53.38,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:03.30,Default,Every,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday Elicia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.88,0:11:10.61,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm, Mr. Hughes? What exactly is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:12.85,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Why, thank you for asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:16.12,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Today is Elicia's birthday, so to speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:17.67,Default,Elicia,0000,0000,0000,,So to speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:22.50,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,So how old are you now, Elicia?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:23.43,Default,Elicia,0000,0000,0000,,Tw-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:26.41,Default,Elicia,0000,0000,0000,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:27.44,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Sh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:28.38,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:30.91,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:45.09,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I've been with them ever since we were little, so they're kind of like my brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:48.26,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,You must always be worried about them with the way they are, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.26,0:11:49.77,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,You bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:53.56,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,They came home after such a long time,\Nand Ed's arm was in pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.27,0:12:01.57,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,And when they called me up, Ed's severely injured...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:03.82,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,...and Al's being troubled by something...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:10.25,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,But they'll never tell me what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:12.64,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Even when they left Resembool...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:16.96,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,They probably didn't feel the need to discuss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:23.59,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,They probably thought that you'd understand, even if they didn't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:31.55,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,But... there are some things in life that will only be understood through words.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:35.34,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's just the way things are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.85,0:12:40.78,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Guys always convey things with actions, not words,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:45.57,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,so if it's something tough, they don't want others to have to put up with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:48.07,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,They don't want to worry people, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:49.34,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,So they don't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:55.82,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,But even then, if those brothers happen to whine...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:59.92,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,...you comfort them and set them straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:02.36,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:08.20,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Elicia, let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:09.70,Default,Elicia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:11.14,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:16.04,Default,Boy2,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Elicia's going to be playing with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:18.19,Default,Boy3,0000,0000,0000,,What? {\i1}I'm{\i0\fscx30} {\r} going to be playing with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:18.88,Default-alt,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Your daughter sure is popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.45,0:13:18.89,Default,Boy4,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:20.65,Default,Boy5,0000,0000,0000,,She's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:23.25,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:26.69,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Do something to my daughter and see what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.69,0:13:28.45,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to convey things with actions {\i1}that{\i0\fscx30} {\r} much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:35.29,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:38.79,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,You can stay here for as long as you're in Central, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:41.34,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,No, that would be too much trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.31,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,She's gotten so attached to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:50.30,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,From this perspective, they almost look like sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:52.35,Default,Elicia,0000,0000,0000,,Winry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:53.85,Default,Elicia,0000,0000,0000,,Have a nice day!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:55.39,Default,Elicia,0000,0000,0000,,Come home soon, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:58.39,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:04.92,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I have a little sister now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:15.12,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So you came again, bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:20.17,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a living body...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:22.88,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,...so you have to drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:27.33,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help that I don't like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:29.73,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually growing, despite how I look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.73,0:14:32.35,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone just calls me puny...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:34.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it easy, Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:38.69,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're so big already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:43.90,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't become like this because I wanted to!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:48.70,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,M-My bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:50.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:53.00,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault we became like this, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:55.65,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want to get your body ba-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:14:58.54,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Is there really a guarantee\NI'll be able to return to my old body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:01.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:02.51,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.51,0:15:04.00,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Believe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:07.51,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to believe with this empty body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:11.13,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Memories are just information if you really think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:14.85,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It should be possible to create them artificially!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:16.75,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What are yo-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:20.77,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, you once told me there was something you couldn't say to me because you were too afraid, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:23.47,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be you were trying to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:30.78,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,...that I'm just a fake... an artificial soul and a set of memories you created?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:38.81,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Winry, you and Granny are both trying to deceive me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:41.75,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right, Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:48.76,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Are those the thoughts you've been holding in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:55.76,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you've got to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:02.67,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:13.93,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Ed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:15.83,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.21,0:16:20.62,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Al, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:23.10,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,IDIOT!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:27.54,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,W-What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:34.75,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Winry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.75,0:16:36.22,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,You moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:39.14,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even know how Ed feels!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:42.89,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,What Ed was afraid to ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:47.58,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,...is whether you hate him or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:53.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's all... my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:17:00.33,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He can't even eat, sleep, or feel pain anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:03.33,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He... He hates me for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:06.58,Default,Pinako,0000,0000,0000,,Al wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:08.33,Default,Pinako,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just ask him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:11.00,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:13.66,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too scared to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.58,0:17:19.74,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,And... And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:21.97,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:30.48,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Just who the heck would be prepared to\Ngive up his life just to create a fake brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:36.71,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you two only have each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:42.70,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Go after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.41,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Y... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:46.41,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,MOVE!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:47.42,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:03.70,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brot-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:09.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, I've gotten a bit rusty because we haven't sparred in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:10.10,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:19.61,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Wha? Wa-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:23.37,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a second, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:25.93,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:29.71,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Your wounds are going to open back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:37.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:40.94,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time in my life, I beat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:45.78,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't fair, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.78,0:18:47.44,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:48.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,A win's a win!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:54.09,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We've always fought a lot, haven't we.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:54.89,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:58.96,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, we fought for the dumbest reasons, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.96,0:19:02.31,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Like who gets to sleep in the top bunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:03.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:05.86,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We fought over snacks, too, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.86,0:19:07.67,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We also fought over toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:09.02,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I won.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.02,0:19:10.79,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we played by Raine River...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:12.96,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You pushed me in, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:15.29,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We fought all the time during our training, too, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.29,0:19:20.38,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That was a draw since Master nearly beat us both to death for being "annoying".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.38,0:19:23.70,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We also fought over who would marry Winry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:25.73,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.73,0:19:28.56,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I won. But she said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:30.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.00,0:19:41.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to tell me all that was a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:42.41,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:45.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We want to return to our bodies, no matter what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:48.63,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to say those feelings are artificial, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:50.66,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,They're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:51.71,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.55,0:19:55.11,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We decided to return to our bodies together, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:57.38,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be moving forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:20:02.18,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If we move forward, we'll get stronger, both physically and mentally.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.78,0:20:04.39,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What about milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:05.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'll drink it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.74,0:20:07.43,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:11.32,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.32,0:20:12.39,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:14.53,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hughes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.10,0:20:19.11,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,There are things that can only be conveyed through words. Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.31,0:20:22.63,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:41.46,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:43.09,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:45.68,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Where... did everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.68,0:20:47.09,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.24,0:20:50.95,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,You're not an Ishbalan, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:53.00,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:55.10,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't introduced myself yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:21:00.61,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a State Alchemist who is going to be in charge of destroying this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.47,0:21:10.24,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.36,0:21:12.69,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.69,0:21:16.04,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the slums on the outskirts of East City.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:20.10,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Sir... you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.10,0:21:23.67,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ishbalan, just like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:27.64,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I won't sell you out or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:31.64,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Are there other Ishbalan survivors in this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:34.09,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,There sure are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:38.37,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Even a soot-covered place like this feels like a city if you live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.37,0:21:44.65,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, "All of this world is within the bosom of our God, Ishvala."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:48.33,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,I... see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:50.70,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:54.12,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,You were floating around in the sewers, covered in wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.61,0:22:03.72,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.72,0:22:06.13,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Is my right arm still attached?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.13,0:22:08.63,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.79,0:22:14.56,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,These tattoos are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.13,0:22:17.06,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.84,0:22:23.28,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,It's a precious bond I received from my family...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.16,0:24:04.25,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Your best friend eventually becomes your comrade-in-arms, and finally, an everyday fixture in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.90,0:24:12.76,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx99}Even if the future you discussed had turned into a shade of lead, your best friend hadn't changed and was always there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.04,0:24:17.89,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.89,0:24:20.89,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 10, Separate Ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.95,0:24:26.02,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,A fixture in one's life. Something like that cannot be replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.02,0:24:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
